object.customQuery:
SELECT InsuredDetail.InsuredKey as InsuredKey, InsuredDetail.PolicyStatus as PolicyStatus, InsuredDetail.InsuredName as InsuredName, InsuredDetail.OriginalInception as OriginalInception, InsuredDetail.InsuredAddress1 as InsuredAddress1, InsuredDetail.InsuredAddress2 as InsuredAddress2, InsuredDetail.InsuredCity as InsuredCity, InsuredDetail.InsuredZip as InsuredZip, InsuredDetail.InsuredHashKey as InsuredHashKey, InsuredDetail.RoweffstrtDt as RoweffstrtDt, InsuredDetail.RowEffEndDt as RowEffEndDt, InsuredDetail.CustomerRef as CustomerRef, InsuredDetail.PolicyKey as PolicyKey, InsuredDetail.InsuredSystemID as InsuredSystemID, InsuredDetail.InsuredId as InsuredId FROM dbo.InsuredDetail
where RowEffEndDt='9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'

object.customQuery:
SELECT Insured_stg.SystemId, Insured_stg.ParentId, Insured_stg.PolicyNumber, case when len(Insured_stg.policversion)='1' then concat('00',Insured_stg.policversion)
             when len(Insured_stg.policversion)='2' then concat('0',Insured_stg.policversion)
             else Insured_stg.policversion end as policversion, Insured_stg.CMMContainer, Insured_stg.Id, Insured_stg.IndexName, Insured_stg.StatusCd, Insured_stg.EntityTypeCd, Insured_stg.PreferredDeliveryMethod, Insured_stg.TemporaryAddressOverrideInd, Insured_stg.NoEmailInd, Insured_stg.InspectionContact, Insured_stg.InspectionContactNumber, Insured_stg.InspectionContactPhoneType, Insured_stg.OriginalInception, Insured_stg.InsuredAddress1, Insured_stg.InsuredAddress2, Insured_stg.InsuredCity, Insured_stg.InsuredZip, Insured_stg.PolicyStatus,
Insured_stg.Addr3,
Insured_stg.Addr4,
Insured_stg.City,
Insured_stg.StateProvCd,
Insured_stg.PostalCode
FROM
 dbo.Insured_stg

object.name: ai
object.customQuery:
SELECT ai.InterestTypeCd as InterestTypeCd, concat(ai.policynumber,ai.policyversion) as PolicyKey from (
select a.interesttypecd,case when length(b.policyversion)='1' then concat('00',b.policyversion)
             when length(b.policyversion)='2' then concat('0',b.policyversion)
             else b.policyversion end as policyversion,b.policynumber from ai a left join basicpolicy b on a.systemid=b.systemid
and a.sequencenumber=b.policyversion and a.parentid=b.parentid where a.cmmcontainer='policy' and b.cmmcontainer='policy')ai--

object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct personinfo_stg.CMMContainer as CMMContainer, personinfo_stg.PersonTypeCd as PersonTypeCd, personinfo_stg.BirthDt as BirthDt, personinfo_stg.SystemId as SystemId FROM dbo.personinfo_stg
where CMMContainer = 'Policy'
and PersonTypeCd in  ('InsuredPersonal', 'OutputInsuredPersonal','InsuredPersonalJoint')
